        "Initial implementation of the terminal module.",
        
        "The terminal has been introduced as a passive system interface within the main dashboard. It is not interactive and does not accept input commands in this version.",
        
        "Core features implemented:",
        "- Boot sequence on initialization",
        "- Typing effect with queued messages",
        "- Scrollable output with persistent session logs",
        "- System message structure (SYS / TIP)",
        "- Integration with main interface events",
        
        "The terminal currently reports:",
        "- System initialization states",
        "- Critical actions (thread creation, reply submission)",
        "- Runtime errors and unavailable modules",
        "- Contextual tips for unavailable features",
        
        "Navigation logs have been intentionally reduced to avoid excessive noise and preserve readability.",
        
        "Future iterations may include:",
        "- User input handling and command system",
        "- Session tracking and timestamps",
        "- Dynamic integration with backend (PHP)",
        "- Context-aware system responses",
        
        "Status: stable"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
